OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkraine rejects Putin's    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChristmas truce            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Russian President Vladimir Putin has   
OL,6, ordered his defence minister to impose 
OL,7, a 36-hour ceasefire on the Ukrainian   
OL,8, front line.                            
OL,10,FThe ceasefire - from 12:00 Moscow time 
OL,11,F(09:00 GMT) - coincides with the       
OL,12,FRussian Orthodox Christmas.            
OL,14,FMr Putin asked Ukraine to reciprocate, 
OL,15,Fbut Kyiv quickly rejected the request. 
OL,17,FUkraine's President Volodymyr Zelensky 
OL,18,Fsaid the truce was an attempt to stop  
OL,19,Fhis country's military advances in the 
OL,20,Feast of the country.                   
